Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.29,Internal or Flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.22,Viet,C,0000,0000,0000,,Ringo-chan, bình tĩnh chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:09.06,Internal or Flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Em xin lỗi, chỉ là em muốn "giả nai" chút thôi.
