Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.95,Internal or Flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Xin lỗi, chỉ là em sock quá thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.56,Viet,C,0000,0000,0000,,Sock à, có chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.83,Internal or Flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Chuyện là, đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:23.84,Viet,R,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan đã... Onii-chan đã...
