Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.92,Viet,As,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, xin lỗi, chém gió đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:47.77,Viet,K,0000,0000,0000,,Chém gió?
